<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Place Disabled</title>
    <style>
        * {
            font-family: Helvetica, Verdana, Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            max-width: 100vw;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            word-break: break-word;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .register {
            margin: 2em 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        a {
            display: inline-block;
            text-align: center;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            background-color: #6610F2;
            padding: 1em;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        a:hover {
            background-color: #520dc2;
        }

        .code {
            background-color: #EADDFF;
            border: 1px solid #EADDFF;
            padding: 1em;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border: 1px solid #000;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        tr {
            border: 1px solid #000;
        }

        th,
        td {
            border: 1px solid #000;
            padding: 0.5em;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #888;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Hello <%= user.first_name %> <%= user.last_name %>,</h1>
    
        <p>We regret to inform you that your place(s) has been disabled. As a result, we had to cancel your booking(s).<br>
            Any lost time quota due to this cancellation will be restored.</p>
            
        <p>We sincerely appologise for the inconvenience.</p>  
        <p>You can visit our website to make a new booking:</p>
            <div class="register">
                <a href="<%= placeBookingURL %>">Click here to book again</a>
            </div>
    
        <p><strong>Booking(s) affected:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <% affectedBookings.forEach(function(booking) { %>
                <li><%= booking.start_time %> - <%= booking.end_time %> (<%= booking.room%>; @<%= booking.place%>)</li>
            <% }); %>
        </ul>
        <p class="footer"><i>This email was auto-generated by the SimpleBooking Tool.</i></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>